column1: # This file defines ChatShop's understanding of Minecraft items.
# Items not defined here will not be understood by ChatShop
# flatly refuse to interact with them.
# ChatShop does not support non-vanilla items.

# Aliases which contain spaces will be logged twice; once with all spaces removed
# once with all spaces replaced by underscores.
